<li><a href="https://www.homefair.com"><strong>HomeFair</strong></a> &ndash; Relocation information, including The Salary Calculator for  cost-of-living comparisons; first-time homebuyer calculators to determine what  you can afford.</li>

<li><a href="https://time.com/money/collection/best-places-to-live-2015/"><strong>Money Magazine - Best Places to Live</strong></a> &ndash; MONEY magazine spent months looking for Great American Towns - where you would want  to raise your children and celebrate life's milestones. Compares 1,300 cities  across America and selects the top ten places to live. </li>

<li><a href="https://www.moving.com/"><strong>Moving.com</strong></a> &ndash; Manage the moving and  relocation process with mortgage quotes and calculators, address change,  utility transfer, city profiling, and self storage information.</li>

