<li><a href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=RIS"><strong>Record  Information Services</strong></a> &ndash; Scroll through public records on new homeowners, new  businesses, bankruptcies, foreclosures and sales for Cook, DuPage, DeKalb, Kane, Kendall,  Lake, McHenry and Will counties.<strong> This  database is available  remotely with your Warrenville Library card number and 4 digit PIN.</strong></li>
  
<li><a href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=RefUSA"><strong>ReferenceUSA  Residential</strong></a> &ndash;  Directory information on over 200 million residences. Search by phone number,  name or address.<strong> </strong><strong>This  database is available  remotely with your Warrenville Library card number and 4 digit PIN. </strong></li>
 
<li><a href="https://www.relocation.com/"><strong>Relocation.com</strong></a> &ndash; Tools to get quotes for movers, storage, insurance, home  improvement, mortgages, and transport in your area. Site  includes a blog and a subscription-only newsletter.</li>

